  "description": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i1.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201204/超实用的英文短信缩写40738.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold;\">J</span><br />\n\t</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\">JAC / JAS &ndash; Just a second</span> <span>等一下</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\">JAM &ndash; Just a minute</span> <span>等一下</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\">JDI &ndash; Just do it</span> <span>做吧！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\">JFF &ndash; Just for fun</span> <span>只是想玩玩，高兴高兴</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\">JIC &ndash; Just in case</span> <span>以防万一</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\">JJ &ndash; Just joking</span> <span>只是开玩笑的</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\">JK &ndash; Just kidding</span> <span>只是逗你玩的</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\">JLMK &ndash; Just let me know</span> <span>到时通知我一下</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\">JTLYK &ndash; Just to let you know</span> <span>只是想通知你一下</span></p>\n<h4>\n\t<span style=\"color: #f00;\">往期回顾（看看你到底掌握了多少呢？）</span></h4>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p361543/\" target=\"_blank\">超实用的英文短信缩写（E开头）<br />\n\t</a></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p361716/\" target=\"_blank\">超实用的英文短信缩写（F开头）<br />\n\t</a></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p362135/\" target=\"_blank\">超实用的英文短信缩写（G开头）<br />\n\t</a></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p362137/\" target=\"_blank\">超实用的英文短信缩写（H开头）</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p364071/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p364071\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p743894/\">奥巴马推荐：这个夏天 我在看这些书</a></li><li sty